''For the French general, see [[Aldebert de Chambrun (1872-1962)]].'' {{Infobox person | name = Aldebert de Chambrun | image = Album des députés au Corps législatif entre 1852-1857-Chambrun.jpg | image_size = | caption = | birth_name = Joseph-Dominique-Aldebert de Pineton, comte de Chambrun | birth_date = November 19, 1821 | birth_place = [[Paris]], France | death_date = February 6, 1899 | death_place = Paris, France | death_cause = | resting_place = | resting_place_coordinates = | residence = | nationality = | other_names = | known_for = | education = | alma mater = | employer = | occupation = Politician | title = | salary = | networth = | term = | predecessor = | successor = | party = | boards = | religion = | spouse = | children = | parents = | relatives = [[Charles de Chambrun (1827-1880)|Charles de Chambrun]] <small>(brother)</small> }} '''Joseph-Dominique-Aldebert de Pineton, comte de Chambrun''' or '''Aldebert de Chambrun''' (1821-1899) was a French politician and businessman.
==Early life== Aldebert de Chambrun was born on November 19, 1821 in [[Paris]], France.<ref name="bnfbio">{{cite web|title=Joseph-Dominique-Aldebert Pineton Chambrun (comte de, 1821-1899)|url=http://data.bnf.fr/12423999/joseph-dominique-aldebert_pineton_chambrun/|website=[[Bibliothèque nationale de France]]|accessdate=August 6, 2016}}</ref><ref name="nassembly">{{cite web|title=Aldebert, Joseph, Dominique Pineton de Chambrun|url=http://www2.assemblee-nationale.fr/sycomore/fiche/(num_dept)/8566|website=National Assembly|accessdate=August 6, 2016}}</ref>
==Career== De Chambrun served as the chairman of [[Baccarat (company)|Baccarat]].<ref name="bnfbio"/> He served as a member of the [[Corps législatif]] from 1857 to 1870, representing [[Lozère]].<ref name="nassembly"/> He served as a member of the [[Chamber of Deputies (France)|Chamber of Deputies]] from 1871 to 1876, representing Lozère.<ref name="nassembly"/> He served as a member of the [[Senate (France)|French Senate]] from 1876 to 1879.<ref name="nassembly"/>
==Death== De Chambrun died on February 6, 1899.<ref name="bnfbio"/><ref name="nassembly"/>
